Package: boolydict
Type: Package
Title: Dictionary search with advanced Boolean operators
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kasper Welbers
Maintainer: Kasper Welbers <kasperwelbers@gmail.com>
Description: Perform dictionary search text analysis with two key benefits.
    Firstly, it supports Boolean operators like AND, OR, NOT, multiword strings, proximity and more.   
    Secondly, these operators can be applied on both full texts and tokenized texts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    data.table,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.7)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppProgress
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
